      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 A practical and affordable ride for the budget-conscious buyer! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives, making it a reliable choice for everyday transportation needs. The exterior shows noticeable signs of wear including scratches and scuffs, and the interior reflects its years of use, but the mechanical fundamentals are there. If you're looking for dependable transportation without the premium price tag, this could be your match!",
