    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2021 Honda Accord in good condition. The interior shows minor signs of use but no significant damage \u2014 upholstery and trim are intact with only light wear, and all controls and displays function properly. The exterior has minor surface scratches or small blemishes but no notable dents or structural damage. Mechanically sound with no known major issues.",
      "price": 33000.0,
